OL,3,CInside story of surgeon who tried to
OL,4,Ckill colleague
OL,6,FIn more than 30 years as a journalist,
OL,7,FI have never covered a trial quite
OL,8,Flike this.
OL,10,FDr Jonathan (Peter) Brooks, 61, was
OL,11,Fconvicted of two counts of attempted
OL,12,Fmurder, attempted arson with intent to
OL,13,Fendanger life, and possession of a
OL,14,Fknife in a public place, after he
OL,15,Fknifed former colleague Graeme Perks
OL,16,Fin the early hours of January 14 2021.
OL,18,FJurors deliberated for more than 12
OL,19,Fhours before finding Brooks guilty of
OL,20,Fall the charges against him.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
