OL,3,CInside story of surgeon who tried to
OL,4,Ckill colleague
OL,6,FThe judge, Mr Justice Pepperall,
OL,7,Fdescribed it as "highly unusual case"
OL,8,Fand for good reason.
OL,10,FFor a start, there was no-one in the
OL,11,Fdock - Dr Jonathan (Peter) Brooks, who
OL,12,Fhas been in prison on remand since
OL,13,F2021, had chosen not to attend his
OL,14,Ftrial.
OL,16,FAnd there was no-one in court
OL,17,Frepresenting him - again, his
OL,18,Fdecision. It meant we were left with a
OL,19,Fcase for the prosecution, but no
OL,20,Fdefence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
