OL,3,CInside story of surgeon who tried to
OL,4,Ckill colleague
OL,6,FSo, some might ask, how could Brooks
OL,7,Fget a fair trial?
OL,9,FMr Justice Pepperall took various
OL,10,Fsteps to address this.
OL,12,FThere was cross-examination of some of
OL,13,Fthe prosecution's witnesses - the
OL,14,Fcourt appointed an advocate to
OL,15,Fquestion the victim Graeme Perks and
OL,16,Fothers about their evidence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
