OL,3,CInside story of surgeon who tried to
OL,4,Ckill colleague
OL,6,FThe reason it's taken four years to
OL,7,Fget to this point is that this case
OL,8,Fhas been beset by delays, adjournments
OL,9,Fand false starts.
OL,11,FThere were no less than nine dates set
OL,12,Ffor the trial, and on five occasions,
OL,13,FBrooks sacked his legal teams.
OL,15,FSometimes, this was due to Brooks'
OL,16,Ffailure to engage with the court
OL,17,Fprocess - he just didn't attend.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
