OL,3,CInside story of surgeon who tried to
OL,4,Ckill colleague
OL,6,FAt other times though it was due to
OL,7,Fhis health - in July 2022, a trial got
OL,8,Funderway, but was halted because
OL,9,FBrooks had developed a painful bone
OL,10,Fcondition in his jaw, a legacy of
OL,11,Ftreatment he'd had for cancer.
OL,13,F"If my choice is between incarceration
OL,14,Fand death, I would rather be dead than
OL,15,Fincarcerated."
OL,17,FWe can now also report that at times
OL,18,Fsince 2021 Brooks has been on hunger
OL,19,Fstrike in prison, claiming he wasn't
OL,20,Fgetting a fair trial.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
