OL,3,CInside story of surgeon who tried to
OL,4,Ckill colleague
OL,6,FHe was refusing to eat as these latest
OL,7,Fproceedings got underway on 10 March.
OL,9,FThe judge ruled that, by doing this,
OL,10,FBrooks was making himself "voluntarily
OL,11,Fabsent" and that the trial should go
OL,12,Fahead without his being present.
OL,14,FIn an extraordinary development,
OL,15,Ftowards the very end of the trial,
OL,16,FBrooks unexpectedly appeared by video
OL,17,Flink from prison.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
