OL,3,CInside story of surgeon who tried to
OL,4,Ckill colleague
OL,6,FThroughout, Mr Justice Pepperall (and
OL,7,Fprevious judges) tried to make
OL,8,Fallowances for Brooks' health and give
OL,9,Fhim the opportunity to fully partake
OL,10,Fin his trial.
OL,12,FThe case was even moved to
OL,13,FLoughborough Court because it had
OL,14,Fbetter wheelchair access than
OL,15,FNottingham, but in the end, it was
OL,16,Ffelt there could be no further delays.
OL,18,FAnd so, after a four-week hearing, the
OL,19,Fjury returned its verdicts, with the
OL,20,Fdock, as it has been throughout this
OL,21,Ftrial, empty.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
